		<item>
		<title>Online Resources</title>
		<link>http://2013-2014.hhsprogramming.com/489/</link>
		<pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2014 19:16:51 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Soroush Nasiriany]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Resources]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://hhsprogramming.com/?p=489</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[*Note: The sources in Bold are highly encouraged Stanford Online All types of Computer Science courses, including web programming, C++, Java, iOS, Algorithms, Cryptology Interactive videos http://online.stanford.edu/courses/topic/4 Khan Academy Mainly web programming https://www.khanacademy.org/cs Code Academy Mainly web programming + Python Very interactive, like a game http://www.codecademy.com/ Code.org Interactive, community based programming Variety of topics http://code.org/ [&#8230;]]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div>*Note: The sources in <strong>Bold</strong> are highly encouraged</div>
<div></div>
<div><strong>Stanford Online</strong></div>
<ul>
<li>All types of Computer Science courses, including web programming, C++, Java, iOS, Algorithms, Cryptology</li>
<li>Interactive videos</li>
<li><a title="http://online.stanford.edu/courses/topic/4" href="http://online.stanford.edu/courses/topic/4" target="_blank">http://online.stanford.edu/courses/topic/4</a></li>
</ul>
<div>Khan Academy</div>
<ul>
<li>Mainly web programming</li>
<li><a title="https://www.khanacademy.org/cs" href="https://www.khanacademy.org/cs" target="_blank">https://www.khanacademy.org/cs</a></li>
</ul>
<div><strong>Code Academy</strong></div>
<ul>
<li>Mainly web programming + Python</li>
<li>Very interactive, like a game</li>
<li><a title="http://www.codecademy.com/" href="http://www.codecademy.com/" target="_blank">http://www.codecademy.com/</a></li>
</ul>
<div>Code.org</div>
<ul>
<li>Interactive, community based programming</li>
<li>Variety of topics</li>
<li><a title="http://code.org/" href="http://code.org/" target="_blank">http://code.org/</a></li>
</ul>
<div>
<div>USACO Training</div>
<ul>
<li>Learn algorithmic techniques</li>
<li>Problem + Grader + Solution</li>
<li><a title="http://cerberus.delos.com:790/usacogate" href="http://cerberus.delos.com:790/usacogate" target="_blank">http://cerberus.delos.com:790/usacogate</a></li>
</ul>
<div><strong>USACO</strong></div>
<ul>
<li>Times, online, programming competition aimed at algorithms</li>
<li>Leads to IOI, international “olympics” of programming</li>
<li><a title="http://www.usaco.org/" href="http://www.usaco.org/" target="_blank">http://www.usaco.org/</a></li>
</ul>
<div>Ideone</div>
<ul>
<li>Compile code for most languages</li>
<li>Not really a course, just a tool</li>
<li><a title="https://ideone.com/" href="https://ideone.com/" target="_blank">https://ideone.com/</a></li>
</ul>
<div><strong>Codechef</strong></div>
<ul>
<li>Very similar to our challenge problems</li>
<li>Good preparation for programming competitions</li>
<li><a title="http://www.codechef.com/" href="http://www.codechef.com/" target="_blank">http://www.codechef.com/</a></li>
</ul>
<p>W3 Schools</p>
<ul>
<li>Web programming tutorials</li>
<li><a title="http://www.w3schools.com/" href="http://www.w3schools.com/">http://www.w3schools.com/</a></li>
</ul>
<p>Learn C++</p>
<ul>
<li><a title="http://www.learncpp.com/" href="http://www.learncpp.com/">http://www.learncpp.com/</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
]]></content:encoded>
